FBIS4-46188 "jptot022__l94098" JPRS-TOT-94-022-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 24 May 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Terrorists Kill Seven Civilians in Southeast Village Raid Terrorists Kill Seven Civilians in Southeast Village Raid TA2405144694 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1430 GMT 24 May 94 TA2405144694 Ankara ANATOLIA English BFN [Text] Baykan, May 24 (A.A) -- Terrorists who raided Ardicli village of Baykan District in southeastern Siirt Province, killed seven people including three children, and wounded another five, it was reported on Tuesday. They escaped after the attack when security forces arrived on the scene of the raid. Officials said that operations were started to catch the terrorists.
